Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.60,0:00:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm a soldier  而那也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.80,0:00:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是被告也是法官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.10,0:00:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我同時站在火線的兩端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.78,0:00:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繞過危險的轉角  追過生與死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.28,0:00:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我奔向前挑戰謊言的影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.15,0:00:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論編織出多少謊言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.76,0:00:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真相還是會照出光明的輪廓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.80,0:00:50.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留著你的眼淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.37,0:00:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.94,0:00:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當我們的痛苦都拋在腦後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.28,0:00:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.98,0:00:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.48,0:01:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是士兵不是站著就是死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.88,0:01:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留著你的眼淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.52,0:01:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佔好你的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.05,0:01:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把它們留給審判之日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.35,0:01:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快速而且自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.96,0:01:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.62,0:01:16.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,犧牲的時候到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.40,0:01:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們只能奮起或是倒地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.20,0:01:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻殼機動隊 S.A.C 2nd GIG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.88,0:01:37.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以上是自衛軍提交的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.52,0:01:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,九州電波塔炸彈處理報告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.86,0:01:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣可以下決定了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.59,0:01:49.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出島應該還有10公斤以上的鈽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.86,0:01:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.70,0:01:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,關於自衛軍的正式出動\N將以下列要項來發表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.77,0:01:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.64,0:02:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是內閣會議的一致見解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.57,0:02:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我無話可說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.18,0:02:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#23  橋落之日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.39,0:02:17.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,內閣會議的進行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.96,0:02:20.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有點過於強度關山的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.26,0:02:23.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們打算不理會由中國政府帶頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.83,0:02:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聯合鄰近亞洲各國所提出的\N應避免使用武力聲明嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.87,0:02:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直拒絕收容難民的國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.64,0:02:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒資格過問這個問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.54,0:02:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.58,0:02:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鄰近國家對我國擴張軍備的疑慮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.25,0:02:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到現在還持續加深…\N對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.98,0:02:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,美帝同樣也有跟我們聯絡喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.52,0:02:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們說不可以讓難民創造出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.55,0:02:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,依靠核武力量贏得獨立的前例
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.86,0:02:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為此  就算要提前簽訂日美安保
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.09,0:02:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也要跟我們合作共同對付這個問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.70,0:02:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什麼時候的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.67,0:03:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我這邊完全不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.30,0:03:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們不信任你這個親中派
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.54,0:03:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來茅葺內閣可能只到攻陷出島為止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.50,0:03:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個混蛋差不多也該注意到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.77,0:03:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.51,0:03:48.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在長崎高速公路的停車場發現被棄置的可疑車輛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.68,0:03:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鈽呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.25,0:03:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.49,0:03:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.05,0:03:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.09,0:03:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能讓媒體知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.46,0:04:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以情報操作為優先
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.66,0:04:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在搶回鈽這件事情上\N請遵照我們的指示來做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.60,0:04:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.70,0:04:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就交給你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.50,0:04:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不必擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.64,0:04:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要照我的指示去做就沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.18,0:04:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在要回辦公廳開始調整事態發展
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.28,0:04:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.96,0:04:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.22,0:04:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在正順利前往Spring 8
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.63,0:04:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.93,0:04:40.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經正式決定出動自衛軍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.50,0:04:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,官房長官7點開記者會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.20,0:04:46.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自衛軍從那時開始出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.21,0:04:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩下不到一小時了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.54,0:04:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現場應該已經開始行動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.18,0:04:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,荒卷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.85,0:04:55.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不明白官房長官有何目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.98,0:05:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想把局勢惡化到這個地步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.02,0:05:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣只會讓狀況陷入泥沼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.26,0:05:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一開戰  出島大概立刻會被攻陷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.43,0:05:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可能成為安保條約締結後的假想敵國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.93,0:05:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是這樣一來跟官房長官\N希望建立軍工復合體的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.00,0:05:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本不一致
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.40,0:05:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,確實如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.64,0:05:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但要是把陷入泥沼本身當作目的\N某種程度上可以理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.94,0:05:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算難民投降  他們也不可能就此消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.35,0:05:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以應該能夠順勢把以往\N處理難民的費用轉到軍備上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.89,0:05:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說也沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.36,0:05:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是來自中國的壓力也會增加啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.46,0:05:46.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來還有我們尚未掌握到的陰謀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.40,0:05:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總理  您覺得這樣可以嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.64,0:05:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了多爭取一點時間\N將聯合國拉進決策當中如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.91,0:06:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.08,0:06:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來陸自在前面設下了檢查哨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.02,0:06:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想他們不會就這樣輕易放我們過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.82,0:06:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.92,0:06:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校  是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.43,0:06:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛剛茅葺總理向聯合國提出核武檢查的要求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.97,0:06:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是順利的話  2天後武檢小組就會到日本來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.94,0:06:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那個時候把鈽交出去的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.77,0:06:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事情很可能就這麼結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.31,0:06:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們能逃到那時候嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.64,0:06:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果躲在某個地方的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.45,0:06:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過  去見武檢小組也是件高難度的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.45,0:06:40.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想辦法順利完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.19,0:06:44.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這或許是我們剩下的最後王牌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.86,0:06:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會盡力去做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.09,0:06:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.96,0:06:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,關於留在本部的新人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.43,0:06:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了以防萬一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.93,0:06:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先設法讓他們跟本案不要有任何關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.77,0:06:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下來都由我們來做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.34,0:06:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.74,0:07:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會先安排的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.74,0:07:03.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,此外  關於塔奇克馬的機體…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.38,0:07:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.88,0:07:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,通訊斷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.22,0:07:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該是緊急狀態法制下所做的局部通信管制吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.69,0:07:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,時間差不多到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.19,0:07:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到會場去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.70,0:07:28.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰爭…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.47,0:07:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要開始了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.11,0:07:36.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聯合國？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.91,0:07:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,茅葺叫來的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.54,0:07:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.48,0:07:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先做好換掉她的準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.25,0:07:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.56,0:07:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開始記者會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.41,0:08:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隨著自衛軍封鎖出島\N鄰近地區也開始大規模交通管制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.09,0:08:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.02,0:08:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將贏得事實上的獨立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.61,0:09:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們要求日本政府
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.95,0:09:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,承認出島是個獨立國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.88,0:09:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣我們就可以進行自由貿易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.69,0:09:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自立自強生活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.92,0:09:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣有什麼不對呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.26,0:09:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們有核武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.53,0:09:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,日本政府承認這個事實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.33,0:09:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是久世同志的行動賜給我們的禮物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.60,0:09:42.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此我們不可能放逐他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.20,0:09:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,此外  攻擊開始前的期限為兩天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.57,0:09:50.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聯合國核武檢查小組的到達將是最後期限
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.54,0:09:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那之前難民如果沒有回應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.78,0:09:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們應該會展開第一波攻擊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.25,0:10:00.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.32,0:10:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開始了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.26,0:10:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在跟課長的聯絡中斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.63,0:10:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們只能靠自己的判斷行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.80,0:10:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過  要不要參加以後的作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.17,0:10:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們可以自由決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.90,0:10:17.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.44,0:10:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼嘛  我們這支獨立傻瓜部隊\N又不是今天才成立的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.71,0:10:25.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,何況只是以自衛軍當對手\N演出逃亡劇不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.21,0:10:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不  我們要帶著鈽到出島去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.48,0:10:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是說出島
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.75,0:10:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.79,0:10:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趁自衛軍進攻之時  一鼓作氣潛入出島
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.42,0:10:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正武檢小組也要來出島
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.23,0:10:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然如此  就在那之前抓到久世\N然後跟鈽一起交給他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.43,0:10:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很有少校的風格讓我只能驚嘆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.97,0:10:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我跟你去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.30,0:10:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.21,0:10:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我當然也一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.88,0:10:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然我沒有意見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.78,0:10:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你反對嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.75,0:11:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.21,0:11:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用薪水範圍內的工作來換刺激\N我當然會做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.25,0:11:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就這麼決定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.79,0:11:13.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,軍方在長崎市街上做了大規模的交通管制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.16,0:11:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隨著這些管制  各國內航線也都全面停飛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.00,0:11:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從這個角度來看  這次政府的決定將是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.44,0:11:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,石川  你的狀況怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.47,0:11:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是少校啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.37,0:11:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是這個樣子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.31,0:11:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偶爾有個這樣的休假也不錯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.21,0:11:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然想跟你這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.08,0:11:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過  現在有件事要拜託你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.21,0:11:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.35,0:11:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要做得到的  什麼事我都幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.32,0:11:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在派了一台塔奇克馬到你那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.85,0:11:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在塔奇克馬的駕駛艙裏面\N有從電波塔回收的一半鈽元素
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.19,0:11:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帶著那個去Spring 8
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.73,0:11:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我懂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.93,0:11:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來是這麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.00,0:11:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這沒問題  不過你們那邊打算怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.94,0:12:00.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們帶著剩下的鈽去出島
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.31,0:12:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說出島？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.84,0:12:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你又想到這麼亂來的手段啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.14,0:12:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,托古薩呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.41,0:12:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟課長在首相官邸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.61,0:12:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.42,0:12:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.72,0:12:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很抱歉我不能參加你那邊\N不過  千萬不要逞強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.52,0:12:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果開始空襲的話\N不知道會演變成什麼狀況喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.73,0:12:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也要小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.20,0:12:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這邊就交給我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.73,0:12:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.07,0:12:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們就在交鈽給聯合國武檢小組\N的新聞畫面上碰頭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.44,0:12:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校  不要死喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.75,0:12:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個…少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.15,0:12:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以問你一件事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.92,0:12:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.12,0:12:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,利用你的外部記憶跟合田談話時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.09,0:12:57.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然覺得這樣做不好\N不過  還是偷看了你對久世的記憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.30,0:12:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.83,0:13:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然沒有看到什麼特別的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.77,0:13:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過  你好像對久世有特別的感情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.27,0:13:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,潛入他腦中時發生了什麼事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.88,0:13:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有發生什麼特別的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.45,0:13:17.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是接觸到他的記憶時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.22,0:13:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,覺得他好像是以前分手的某個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.75,0:13:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前分手的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.56,0:13:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過  是很久以前的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.03,0:13:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,差不多快到了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.71,0:13:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰車真的會攻過來嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.78,0:13:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我們這邊可是有不惜自爆的覺悟啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.58,0:13:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,久世同志不是說什麼都不要做嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.95,0:13:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們這邊絕對不可以出手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.39,0:13:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣國際輿論就會站在我們這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.86,0:14:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這場爭鬥如果以不戰收場  我們就勝利了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.90,0:14:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好好去跟久世連線吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.15,0:14:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是久世英雄吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.28,0:14:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.76,0:14:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在那邊看過你一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.73,0:14:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.83,0:14:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在台灣有很多人圍在你旁邊\N在出島卻很少人知道你的長相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.44,0:14:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為這裏電子腦化的人很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.71,0:14:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.68,0:14:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是靠網絡對難民傳播思想啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.48,0:14:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.08,0:15:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這可得要有持續回答300萬人詢問的精神力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.36,0:15:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才做得到的神跡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.66,0:15:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.79,0:15:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這也有陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.16,0:15:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陷阱？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.07,0:15:14.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.30,0:15:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,水往低處流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.40,0:15:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人心也一樣流往低處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.74,0:15:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.64,0:15:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,解析分離思想病毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.54,0:15:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回到出島之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.38,0:15:29.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很多難民馬上就跟我連線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.95,0:15:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我從那時就決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.65,0:15:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我唯一的行動準則就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.72,0:15:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重視他們的意志  並且幫助他們完成願望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.92,0:15:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此成為他們的領導者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.13,0:15:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實並不會十分困難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.33,0:15:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其它的意識則加上過濾器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.17,0:15:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,努力將不斷與我連線的難民意識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.70,0:15:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟我懷抱的理想同步化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.91,0:15:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大戰之後我在歐亞大陸上徘徊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.41,0:16:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尋找個人在系統中的存在意義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.08,0:16:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那旅程當中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.75,0:16:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難民教導我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.98,0:16:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人本來就是一種需要他人介入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.75,0:16:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才有可能生存的生物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.66,0:16:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把自己的義務和權利放在天秤上比較
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.09,0:16:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要不在權利上先添加砝碼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.20,0:16:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算遵從社會上的規則  也不會迷失自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.34,0:16:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.41,0:16:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然這個普遍的思想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.65,0:16:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感覺上非常容易接受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.22,0:16:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是那些難民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.05,0:16:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一旦開始瞭解網絡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.05,0:16:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道階級統治有上層的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.62,0:16:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就會忘記那個思想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.19,0:16:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全部往低處流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.03,0:16:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就像有了力量就想要誇耀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.76,0:16:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拿到武器就想用一次看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.97,0:16:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你明明知道這些\N那為什麼要把局勢弄到這個地步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.14,0:17:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真的以為革命這種牢騷話可以輕易達成嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.34,0:17:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.61,0:17:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.78,0:17:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我所想的革命還要稍微更進一步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.02,0:17:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在只是讓人們走向「上部構造」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.02,0:17:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我革命目標的前階段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.59,0:17:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上部構造？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.73,0:17:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那跟階級統治不一樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.53,0:17:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的  不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.93,0:17:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在覆蓋這個地上的網絡\N已經變成下部構造
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.04,0:17:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是它的本來目的已然終止\N正在創造另一種意義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.54,0:17:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然還無法從網絡中分離\N不過  相對於這個基礎的下部構造
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.71,0:17:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,確實有全新意義的反作用力存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.35,0:17:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並且昇華成上部構造
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.03,0:18:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是我所思考的革命定義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.03,0:18:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然聽不太懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.50,0:18:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過  你能將這個跟難民共享嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.74,0:18:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該已經有潛在性的共享
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.74,0:18:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過  具體上還沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.55,0:18:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我以前也因為對「人」的興趣\N而辭去官位來到民間
